	<title>Sensor and User Management Module</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>3. Sensor and User Management Module</h1>
<h3><p>This module allows the administrator to manage the sensors and the user information.</p></h3>

<div id="3.1">
<h2>3.1 Register New User</h2>
<h3><p>System administrator can register new users for the Ocean Observation System.</p></h3>
<h3><p>Clicking the "<b><em>Add an user</em></b>" hyperlink will navigate the system administrator to the <em>New User Register</em> page.</p></h3>
<h3><p>You need to provide the following information:</p></h3>
<ul>
	<li>User Name</li>
	<li>Password</li>
	<li>User Class*</li>
	<li>Choose Person*</li>
</ul>
<h3><p>* <span class="code">Choose one from "Administrator", "Scientist", "Data Curator"</span>.</br>
* <span class="code">Choose a Person from the database. See <a href="3_user_management_module.html#3.3">3.3 Register New Person</a> and <a href="3_user_management_module.html#3.4">3.4 Update Personal Information</a> for more information</span>.</p></h3>
<h3><p>Click the "<b><em>Add</em></b>" button to register. Click the "<b><em>cancel</em></b>" button to cancel the registration.</p></h3>
</div>

<div id="3.2">
<h2>3.2 Remove An User</h2>
<h3><p>System administrator can remove new users for the Ocean Observation System.</p></h3>
<h3><p>Clicking the "<b><em>Remove an user</em></b>" hyperlink will navigate the system administrator to the <em>Manage Account</em> page.</p></h3>
<h3><p>Click the "<b><em>Remove</em></b>" button to remove this user.
</div>

<div id="3.3">
<h2>3.3 Enter and Update User Information Page</h2>
<h3><p>System administrators can enter the page which includes all information about users in the Ocean Observation System and manage all users information in this page.</p></h3>
<h3><p>Enter the user name and click the "<b><em>GO</em></b>" button. System administrator will be navagate to the "Manage Account" page and able to manage user's account. </p></h3>
<h3><p>You can only change:</p></h3>
<ul>
	<li>Password</li>
</ul>
<h3><p>Click the "<b><em>Update</em></b>" button to save the changes.</p></h3>
<h3><p>If administrators refuse to save the previous changes, click the "<b><em>Cancel</em></b>" button to give up the changes. </p></h3>
</div>

<div id="3.4">
<h2>3.4 Register New Person</h2>
<h3><p>System administrators can register new person for the Ocean Observation System.</p></h3>
<h3><p>Clicking the "<b><em>Add a Person</em></b>" hyperlink will navigate system administrator to the New Person Register page.</p></h3>
<h3><p>You need to provide the following information:</p></h3>
<ul>
	<li>Last Name</li>
	<li>First Name</li>
	<li>Address</li>
	<li>Email*</li>
	<li>Phone number</li>
	<li>Password</li>
</ul>
<h3><p><span class="code">* Note that the Email should be unique, which means that a person cannot have the same Email with any other person in the database.</span></p></h3>
<h3><p>Click the "<b><em>Add</em></b>" button to register. Click the "<b><em>cancel</em></b>" button to cancel the registration.</p></h3>
</div>

<div id="3.5">
<h2>3.5 Update Personal Information</h2>
<h3><p>System administrator can update the personal information in the Ocean Observation System.</p></h3>
<h3><p>Select a person and click the "<b><em>GO</em></b>" button. System administrator will be able to manage personal information of this person. </p></h3>
<h3><p>You can change any of the following fields:</p></h3>
<ul>
	<li>Last Name</li>
	<li>First Name</li>
	<li>Address</li>
	<li>Email*</li>
	<li>Phone number</li>
	<li>Password</li>
</ul>
<h3><p><span class="code">* Note that the Email should be unique, which means that a person cannot have the same Email with any other perseon in our database.</span></p></h3>
<h3><p>Click the "<b><em>UPDATE</em></b>" button to save the changes.</p></h3>
</div>

<div id="3.6">
<h2>3.6 Remove a Person</h2>
<h3><p>System administrators can remove person from the Ocean Observation System.</p></h3>
<h3><p>Clicking the "<b><em>Remove a Person</em></b>" hyperlink will navigate system administrator to the <em>Manage Account</em> page.</p></h3>
<h3><p>Administrators need to select a person to remove from Ocean Observation System</p></h3>
<h3><p>Click the "<b><em>Remove</em></b>" button to remove.
</div>

<div id="3.7">
<h2>3.7 Register New Sensor</h2>
<h3><p>System administrator can register new sensor for the Ocean Observation System.</p></h3>
<h3><p>Clicking the "<b><em>Add a sensor</em></b>" hyperlink will navigate the system administrator to the <em>New Sensor Register</em> page.</p></h3>
<h3><p>You need to provide the following information:</p></h3>
<ul>
	<li>sensor_id</li>
	<li>location</li>
	<li>sensor_type</li>
	<li>description*</li>
</ul>
<h3><p>* <span class="code">description is option, administrator can update this information later</span>.</br>
</div>

<div id="3.8">
<h2>3.8 Remove a Sensor</h2>
<h3><p>System administrators can remove sensor from the Ocean Observation System.</p></h3>
<h3><p>Clicking the "<b><em>Remove a sensor</em></b>" hyperlink will navigate system administrator to the <em>Manage Sensor</em> page.</p></h3>
<h3><p>Administrators need to select a sensor to remove from Ocean Observation System</p></h3>
<h3><p>Click the "<b><em>Remove</em></b>" button to remove.
</div>


